These are Puzzles for 7x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-4-1::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: july, august
There are 2 different favourite colors: pink, lavender
2 different games are played: poker, monopoly
House: cape-cod, tower
City: edinburgh, new-york
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: davidoff, bongani
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: iris, balloon-flower
1. the person who likes lavender is on the left of the person who growsiris##1
2. the bongani-smoker is in an odd position##4
3. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person playing poker##1
4. the tower house is on the left of the person traveling to edinburgh##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |
| Birthday      | august     | july |
| Color         | lavender  | pink       |
| Game           | monopoly   | poker    |
| House   | tower     | cape-cod   |
| City   | new-york      | edinburgh     |
| Cigar         | bongani | davidoff      |
| Flower     | balloon-flower       | iris           |

