.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-4-2::.
City: venice, paris
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: august, may
2 different games are played: billiard, chess
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-henry, prince
There are 2 different favourite colors: mauve, yellow
The people have 2 different hobbies: sudoku, hiking
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: basketball, snowboarding
1. the old-henry-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1
3. the prince-smoker is in an odd position##4
4. the person who likes yellow is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
5. the person traveling to venice is in an even position##4
6. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2      |
| City      | paris         | venice       |
| Birthday          | august        | may |
| Game           | chess | billiard    |
| Cigar   | prince        | old-henry  |
| Color   | yellow        | mauve       |
| Hobby           | hiking            | sudoku        |
| Sport     | snowboarding            | basketball       |

