2. the person traveling to liverpool is in an even position##4
3. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left of the person eating grapefruit##1
4. the person playing scrabble is in an odd position##4
5. the person traveling to liverpool is the palace house##1
6. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |
| Game      | scrabble    | bridge   |
| Birthday         | september | april |
| House   | ranch-style      | palace     |
| Nationality   | indonesian        | german        |
| Flower           | amaryllis        | orchid |
| City         | boston    | liverpool |
| Food     | cauliflower         | grapefruit       |

