3. the person eating spinach is the bongani-smoker##1
4. the person who growsdaisy is the person who's birthday is in march##1
5. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in february##3
6. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |
